wikipedia_page.main: Jabez W. "Jack" White (born 1879) is a former footballer who played as a full back for Leeds City in the Football League. He also played for Ollenshaw United, Grays Anchor, Swanscombe, Grays United, Queens Park Rangers and Merthyr Town.

response: Jack White (born 1975) is an American musician and singer-songwriter.
